"use strict";(self["webpackChunkmyblog"]=self["webpackChunkmyblog"]||[]).push([[62518],{62518:function(n,r,e){e.r(r),r["default"]='## **3. 枚举类型**\r\n\r\n枚举类型（`enum`）是一种用于定义一组命名常量的类型。\r\n\r\n### **3.1 枚举的定义与使用**\r\n\r\n#### **1. 定义**\r\n\r\n- 使用 `enum` 关键字定义枚举类型。\r\n- **语法**：\r\n\r\n  ```c\r\n  enum enumeration_name {\r\n      value1,\r\n      value2,\r\n      ...\r\n  };\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 示例：\r\n\r\n  ```c\r\n  enum Weekday {\r\n      Monday,\r\n      Tuesday,\r\n      Wednesday,\r\n      Thursday,\r\n      Friday,\r\n      Saturday,\r\n      Sunday\r\n  };\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n- 默认情况下，枚举值从 `0` 开始递增：\r\n  - `Monday = 0`, `Tuesday = 1`, ..., `Sunday = 6`\r\n\r\n#### **2. 使用**\r\n\r\n- 示例：\r\n\r\n  ```c\r\n  enum Weekday today = Wednesday;\r\n  if (today == Wednesday) {\r\n      printf("Today is Wednesday.\\n");\r\n  }\r\n  ```\r\n\r\n---'}}]);
